@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

title rigol2ltspice - Usage and Data Flow

actor User
rectangle "rigol (CLI)" as CLI
file "Rigol CSV\n(input)" as IN
file "LTspice Text\n(output)" as OUT

User --> CLI : run ./rigol <in.csv> <out.txt> [shift_ms]
IN --> CLI : read CSV rows
CLI --> CLI : skip first 2 lines
CLI --> CLI : parse first 2 fields\n(time, value)
CLI --> CLI : apply shift\n(explicit or auto)
CLI --> OUT : write "time value" rows
CLI --> User : done / status logs

note right of CLI
Shift rules:
1) If shift_ms provided,
   use shift_ms / 1000.
2) Else if first time < 0,
   shift so first output time = 0.
end note
@enduml
